---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout title="About | boim.thinks()">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 py-12">
    
    
    <article>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>
      
      <div class="prose-custom">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Hi, I'm Chris Pennington, a developer and tech enthusiast who loves building things with code.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Welcome to my digital garden! This is where I share my thoughts on technology, programming, 
          and anything else that catches my interest. I believe in learning in public and documenting 
          my journey as I explore new technologies and solve interesting problems.
        </p>
        
        <h2>What I Do</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          I work on a variety of projects ranging from web development to automation tools. 
          My goal is to create solutions that are not only functional but also delightful to use.
        </p>
        
        <ul class="mb-6">
          <li class="mb-2">Full-stack web development</li>
          <li class="mb-2">Open source contributions</li>
          <li class="mb-2">Technical writing and documentation</li>
          <li class="mb-2">Mentoring new developers</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Feel free to reach out if you'd like to collaborate on a project, have questions about 
          something I've written, or just want to chat about tech. You can find me on various platforms:
        </p>
        
        <ul class="mb-6">
          <li class="mb-2">
            <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
               class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">
              GitHub
            </a> - Code and projects
          </li>
          <li class="mb-2">
            <a href="https://twitter.com/yourusername" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
               class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">
              Twitter
            </a> - Quick thoughts and updates
          </li>
          <li class="mb-2">
            <a href="mailto:youremail@example.com" 
               class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">
              Email
            </a> - For longer discussions
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>